description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 44, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 88, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, Stringalong for South, and 5 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60442-65750-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [88 Votes, Common]
